File:Tōka-ebisu Jinja shintō shrine honden 7-1 Higashikōen Hakata-ku Fukuoka City 20221115.jpg|Main hall
</gallery>

== Tōka Ebisu New Year's festival ==
Every year, a grand festival is held from {{ill|January 8|ja|1月8日}} to {{ill|January 11|ja|1月11日}}. The 8th is called "Hatsu Ebisu," the 9th is "Yoi Ebisu," the 10th is the "Main festival," and the 11th is "Nokori Ebisu." During the New Year's festival, events like lotteries and {{ill|Geisha|ja|芸妓}} processions are famous.

== Access ==
*{{ill|Fukuoka City Subway Hakozaki Line|ja|福岡市地下鉄箱崎線}} {{ill|Chiyo-Kenchōguchi Station|ja|千代県庁口駅}}
